project:
When you are typing expressions into the boxes you can type the following:
    • [b]Numbers[/b] (EX. 7   2.5   3.14159  etc.)
    • [b]+ - * / [/b] for add, subtract, multiply, and divide.
    • [b]**[/b] for exponents. (EX: 4**2 = 16 or 4**0.5 = 2)
    • [b]Variable Names[/b] Make new variables using box to left.
    • [b]time[/b] for the time in sec. since the simulation began.
    • [b]dt[/b] for the time it takes the code to repeat. (~1/60sec)
